*MDDocumentLineEditor*
*&lt;&lt;ThemeWidget&gt;&gt;*
--
*Referencias*
+line_state: LineState  // BIND DIRECTO a Properties
+operations: DocumentOperations
+index: int
--
*Sub-widgets*
+wg_line_editor: MDLineEditor
+wg_number_line: Optional[MDDLNumberLine]
--
*Bindings a LineState (automáticos)*
_bind_to_line_state():
    state.bind(active=self._on_active_changed)
    state.bind(editing=self._on_editing_changed)
    state.bind(selected=self._on_selected_changed)
    state.bind(hotlight=self._on_hotlight_changed)
    state.bind(visible=self._on_visible_changed)
    state.bind(height=self._on_height_changed)
--
*Callbacks de Properties (UI reactiva)*
-_on_active_changed(instance, value)
-_on_editing_changed(instance, value)
-_on_selected_changed(instance, value)
-_on_hotlight_changed(instance, value)
-_on_visible_changed(instance, value)
-_on_height_changed(instance, value)
--
*Eventos → Operations (TODOS)*
-_on_click(touch)  // → operations.activate_line()
-_on_text_changed(text)  // → operations.update_line_text()
-_on_mouse_enter()  // → operations.set_hotlight(True)
-_on_mouse_leave()  // → operations.set_hotlight(False)
--
*Visualización*
+update_visual_state()</panel_attributes>
