*Flujo V6: Tecla Enter (nueva línea)*
--
1. MDDocumentEditor._handle_enter()
2. → operations.insert_line_below(active_index, "")
3. → state_manager.insert_line(index, new_md_line)
4. → state_manager.dispatch('on_line_added', event)
5. → MDDocumentEditor._on_line_added(inst, event)
6. → crea nuevo MDDocumentLineEditor
7. → nuevo widget hace bind() a su LineState</panel_attributes>
