*Flujo V6: Filtrar por texto*
--
1. InputSearchOrFilter.filter_toggle → state='toggled'
2. → App._on_filter_state_change(instance, state)
3. → operations.filter_by_text(text, include_parents)
4. → Para cada línea:
      state_manager.update_state(i, visible=match)
5. → LineState.visible = True/False
6. → Kivy dispara on_visible
7. → MDDocumentLineEditor._on_visible_changed()
8. → widget.opacity/disabled actualizado</panel_attributes>
