*Flujo V6: Limpiar filtro*
--
1. InputSearchOrFilter.filter_toggle → state='untoggled'
2. → App._on_filter_state_change(instance, state)
3. → operations.clear_filter()
4. → Para cada línea:
      state_manager.update_state(i, visible=True)
5. → LineState.visible = True
6. → Kivy dispara on_visible
7. → MDDocumentLineEditor._on_visible_changed()
8. → widget visible</panel_attributes>
